          </ol>
          <h3 class="text-white text-[32px] font-bold my-4">Why Choose Us?</h3>
          <ul class="text-[17px] list-disc ml-7">
            <li>
              <span class="text-white font-bold">Tailored Solutions:</span>
              We customize every strategy to align with your business goals.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="text-white font-bold">Creative Expertise:</span>
              Our designs are purpose-driven and aligned with your brand identity.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="text-white font-bold">Results-Oriented:</span>
              We focus on delivering measurable growth and success.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="text-white font-bold">Collaborative Approach:</span>
              We work closely with you to bring your vision to life.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class="text-white text-[32px] font-bold mt-7 mb-4">Mission</h3>
          <p class="flex flex-col text-[17px]">
            <span
